### -------------------------------------------------------
### Frontend Discovery Service — Consumer API
### -------------------------------------------------------
### Public endpoints (no auth required).
### The host app and discovery-proxy call these at runtime.
### -------------------------------------------------------


### =====================
### Staging
### =====================

### Get staging manifest (all MFEs with active versions)
GET {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_CONSUMER_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv STAGING_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends

###

### =====================
### Production
### =====================

### Get production manifest
GET {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_CONSUMER_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv PRODUCTION_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends

###

### =====================
### Local Discovery Proxy
### =====================

### Get local manifest (staging with local overrides)
GET http://localhost:4300/microFrontends
